## Validation Configuration

### Local Validation (runs on host machine)
```yaml
validation:
  local:
    - name: "lint"
      command: "{{LINT_COMMAND}}"
      required: true
    - name: "typecheck"
      command: "{{TYPECHECK_COMMAND}}"
      required: true
    - name: "test:unit"
      command: "{{TEST_UNIT_COMMAND}}"
      required: true
    - name: "test:e2e"
      command: "{{TEST_E2E_COMMAND}}"
      required: false
    - name: "build"
      command: "{{BUILD_COMMAND}}"
      required: true
```

### Docker Validation (runs in container)
```yaml
  docker:
    enabled: {{true | false}}
    image: "{{DOCKER_IMAGE}}"
    commands:
      - name: "lint"
        command: "{{DOCKER_LINT_COMMAND}}"
      - name: "typecheck"
        command: "{{DOCKER_TYPECHECK_COMMAND}}"
      - name: "test"
        command: "{{DOCKER_TEST_COMMAND}}"
      - name: "build"
        command: "{{DOCKER_BUILD_COMMAND}}"
```

